data.description: Established neighborhood, a variety of excellent shopping around area, very nice BRICK home, MOVE-IN READY, shed under construction in back fenced yard, large residential subdivision lot, Room sizes approximate, use due diligence, all offers considered, huge yard, porch behind house, large shade tree in back yard, large two car garage, fenced yard, no HOA, property just minutes from Strawberry Park, San Jacinto College, Sam Houston Tollway, Highway 225, I-45, Hobby Airport.
